            "description": "In San Francisco, Freed, the AI clinician assistant utilized by over 26,000 clinicians and institutions spanning 100+ specialties, introduced Freed Front Desk. This AI-powered receptionist handles clinic calls 24/7, records each patient request, and sends structured summaries to staff via a shared inbox. It achieves a 90% drop in hold times, eliminates voicemails, and needs no IT setup. Freed's AI scribe, launched in 2023, provided significant assistance to clinicians.",
